N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 441.93 - Direct expense

State Regulations

The cost of any good or service that contributes to, and
is readily ascribable to, product or service output. Direct expense includes
salaries and wages, employee benefits, professional fees, supplies, purchased
services, other direct expenses and transfers. Notes
